data.description: Move in ready country home sitting on nearly 3 acres with OWNED SOLAR. When you walk into this home you will notice the ceramic wood tile floors and the brand new remodeled kitchen. The kitchen overlooks the living room as well as a large eat in kitchen dining space. The kitchen offers new kitchen cabinets, new backspash, new stainless steel appliances, and a large walk in pantry with bard door. Off of the kitchen area you can find an additional flex space that can be easily turned into another bedroom or office. Down the hall you can find the guest bathroom that has a brand new vanity and fixtures. Down the hall you can find three bedrooms one of the guest bedrooms offers a walk in closet. At the end of the hall you can find your master bedroom is a good size and offers dual sinks. AC unit, roof and windows are all newer. This land has so many possibilities. Behind the home is a soccer field. Home has Lakeside irrigation water rights
